Invocation Name: avocado challenge
des:
We all know the health benefits of fruits and vegetables. This is a game where you can name and learn many fruits and vegetables, their healthy values and fun facts about them. We have prepared interesting descriptions of each one to help you level up. If you get stuck you can use the hints or skip the word and come back to it later. Let's get started and have fun!

Disclaimer: The information in this skill is provided for informational and educational purposes only.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
